advantages of TestNG

-> Datadriven testing with @DataProvider
->Annotations make test writing easy amd structured
-> Parallel test execution to save time.
->Flexible test configuration(using testng.xml)

@BeforeMethod(3rd)
@BeforeClass(2nd)
@BeforeSuite(1st)
@Test(4th)
@AfterMethod(5)
@AfterClass(6)
@AfterSuite(7)
@DataProvider
@Paramter will work only with @Test annotation

Read the configuration properties file to load test settings and use those settings to initialize and control the Selenium WebDriver.
